                <!-- Section 3 -->
                <section id="section-3" class="mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">3. Qi Certification Process Step-by-Step</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">The Qi cert process has several key steps. It usually takes 8-16 weeks. Working with an experienced <a href="/service" class="text-brandBlue hover:text-brandOrange font-semibold">OEM/ODM partner</a> can speed things up a lot.</p>
                    
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-brandBlue/20"></div>
                        <div class="space-y-8">
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <div class="absolute left-6 w-6 h-6 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-black">1</div>
                                <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase mb-2">Join the WPC</h4>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-2">Sign up as a WPC member at <a href="https://www.wirelesspowerconsortium.com/membership/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brandBlue hover:text-brandOrange font-semibold">wirelesspowerconsortium.com</a>. Fees range from $2,500 (small firm) to $15,000+ (big maker). Your member level decides your access to working groups and early spec updates.</p>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Duration:</strong> 1-2 weeks for application approval.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <div class="absolute left-6 w-6 h-6 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-black">2</div>
                                <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase mb-2">Product Registration</h4>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-2">Submit your product details through the WPC member portal. Include design specs, power class (5W to 65W), coil setup, and target device types.</p>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Duration:</strong> 1-3 days.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <div class="absolute left-6 w-6 h-6 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-black">3</div>
                                <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase mb-2">Sample Preparation</h4>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-2">Make samples that match your final product exactly —same parts, same PCB, same firmware. Any difference between test samples and final units will void your cert.</p>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-6 weeks depending on product complexity.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <div class="absolute left-6 w-6 h-6 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-black">4</div>
                                <h4 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase mb-2">Authorized Laboratory Testing</h4>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-2">Send samples to a WPC-accredited Qi test lab. Tests cover power efficiency, FOD, temperature control, EMF, and cross-device fit. Browse our <a href="/products/wireless-charger" class="text-brandBlue hover:text-brandOrange font-semibold">Qi-certified wireless charger collection</a> to see products that have passed these tests.</p>
