                                    <td class="p-4 text-slate-600">Must detect and respond to metal objects (coins, keys) within specified time limits; varies by power class.</td>
                                    <td class="p-4 text-red-600">Fire risk, safety hazard, product recall.</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200">
