                                    <td class="p-4 text-slate-600">Must work correctly with reference Qi receivers and at least three different certified transmitter devices.</td>
                                    <td class="p-4 text-red-600">Failed certification, interoperability issues.</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200">
                                    <td class="p-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Power Class Compliance.</td>
                                    <td class="p-4 text-slate-600">Must meet all requirements specific to declared power class (BPP, EPP, MPP)</td>
