                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">7. Qi2 vs Qi Certification Differences</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6"><a href="https://www.wirelesspowerconsortium.com/blog/the-future-of-wireless-charging-qi2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brandBlue hover:text-brandOrange font-semibold">Qi2</a> launched in 2023 as a big step up in wireless charging. Here are the key differences between Qi (v1.x) and Qi2 to help with product planning.</p>
                    
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
                        <table class="w-full border border-slate-200 rounded-xl">
                            <thead class="bg-slate-100">
                                <tr>
                                    <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-sm">Feature</th>
                                    <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-sm">Qi (BPP/EPP)</th>
                                    <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-sm">Qi2 (MPP)</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200">
                                    <td class="p-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Magnetic Alignment.</td>
