                        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                            <p><strong class="text-brandOrange">Qi (BPP/EPP):</strong> Best for budget chargers, car mounts, furniture integration, and markets where Qi2 accessories aren't prevalent. Lower certification costs.</p>
                            <p><strong class="text-brandOrange">Qi2 (MPP):</strong> Best for premium chargers targeting iPhone 12+ users, magnetic accessories (power banks, stands), and future-proofing your product line.</p>
